{"word":"παραρτέομαι","slug":"παραρτέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραρτέομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>ionic Verb\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:ἀρτέομαι'><el>ἀρτέομαι</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>:<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to fit out for oneself</i>, <el>παραρτέετο στρατιήν</el> <i>was engaged in preparing his</i> army, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <i>to hold oneself in readiness</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}